# Media AIMD Test

This fixture validates a local media block and an inline media reference such as {{ref_media|lecture_video}}.

{{step|review_media}} Confirm that the media block can be rendered and optionally pinned by the host.

```media
id: lecture_video
kind: video
src: files/lecture.mp4
mime: video/mp4
poster: files/lecture-poster.jpg
title: Lecture Video
legend: A local video resource packaged with the AIMD protocol.
```
